OL,3,CNo final inquest date two years after
OL,4,Cparachutist fell to his death
OL,6,FA final inquest date is still to be
OL,7,Ffinalised more than two years after a
OL,8,Fvideographer died during a parachute
OL,9,Fjump.
OL,11,FSam Cornwell, 46, from Hampshire, was
OL,12,Ffilming another skydiver near Shotton
OL,13,Fairfield in County Durham in April
OL,14,F2024 when his main parachute failed to
OL,15,Fopen properly.
OL,17,FHe suffered critical injuries and was
OL,18,Fpronounced dead at the scene at South
OL,19,FWest Industrial Estate near Peterlee.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/3
