OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1777471868
OL,3,CNo final inquest date two years after
OL,4,Cparachutist fell to his death
OL,6,FA brief inquest hearing in Crook,
OL,7,FCounty Durham, on Tuesday was told
OL,8,Fthat a "parallel investigation" by
OL,9,FDurham County Council into what
OL,10,Fhappened that day was ongoing.
OL,12,FCoroner Jeremy Chipperfield was told
OL,13,Fthat the jump operators, Sky-High
OL,14,FSkydiving, had requested more time to
OL,15,Fanswer the council's questions.
OL,17,FMr Chipperfield adjourned the case
OL,18,Funtil June 2 to allow the council to
OL,19,Fupdate his coroner's officer with any
OL,20,Frelevant information.
