OL,3,CNo final inquest date two years after
OL,4,Cparachutist fell to his death
OL,6,FIn October, the coroner apologised to
OL,7,Fthe mother of Mr Cornwell's children
OL,8,Ffor delays in concluding the hearing.
OL,10,FHe told Leni Boudewijn back then: "A
OL,11,Flong time has passed and I regret it
OL,12,Fhas not been possible to provide
OL,13,Fclosure before now, but it is
OL,14,Fnecessary to do things properly."
